Title: Tinkle-monks
Description:
Nothing like smacking snapjaws with your keytar. 

This mod adds:
-keytar: a fire-based cudgel 
-Tinkle-monk: companion-oriented subtype, starts with a keytar
-Pluna Freyk: custom start with a fancy beaked tile -Tambourine Gal: a telepathic Tinkle-monk to accompany you on your adventures

Have fun!
